              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Loud noises during spin:</strong> bearing or suspension issues</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Washer not draining:</strong> clogged filter or drain pump malfunction</li>
